{"tid":27041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼蘇門答臘北部M6.5地震，至少25死","createTime":"2016-12-07T05:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T09:51:35.000Z","uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3574f16607df7ead810cd118d5c8f961d6123b68","tid":27041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"印尼蘇門答臘島北部亞齊省（Aceh）外海今天發生規模6.5強震。當地救災機構表示，截止目前為止，共有25人喪生，較稍早統計的死亡人數增加。<br />\n<br />\n美國地質調查所指出，這次淺層地震於5時3分發生，震央在魯勒特鎮（Reuleuet）北方約10公里處。目前未發布海嘯警報。<br />\n<br />\n位於震央附近、災情最慘重的畢迪賈雅縣（Pidie Jaya）救災機構主管普特馬那夫（Puteh Manaf）表示，目前死亡人數已經攀升至25人，死者大多是畢迪賈雅縣及附近地區的民眾，大部分是因為地震造成建築物崩塌所致。<br />\n<br />\n畢迪賈雅縣副縣長薩伊德（Said Mulyadi）表示，許多重機具已陸續進駐畢迪賈雅縣協助搜救，縣府也會持續向鄰近地方政府尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n受創最重的畢迪賈雅縣（Pidie Jaya）副縣長穆雅迪（Mulyadi）說：「這裡的醫院容納不下更多傷者了，因此我們將部分傷者送往鄰近地區。」<br />\n<br />\n畢迪賈雅縣目前初步估計有數百間房屋受損，分布在尤里（Ulee Gle）、班達爾杜阿（Bandar Dua Sub）、魯恩（Lueng Putu）、班達爾巴魯（Bandar Baru）等地。<br />\n<br />\n37歲的地方居民賈雅（Hasbi Jaya）說，強震來襲時他的家人正在睡夢中，地震一來，「我們隨即跑出屋外，不過房子馬上倒塌，從屋頂到地板，所有東西全倒了，也都毀了。我望向身旁，所有鄰居的房子也全塌了」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲「雪梨晨驅報」（The Sydney Morning Herald）報導，印尼國家防災管理署（BNPB）的努格羅厚（Sutopo Nugroho）聲明說：「地震感覺相當強烈，許多人倉皇逃出門外，因為房子倒塌了。」<br />\n<br />\n亞齊省印尼紅十字會負責人魯迪安托（Rudianto）說：「有些建築物已被夷為平地。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nd1xfrzt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnd1xfrzt&h=91045fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oz1hwuts\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foz1hwuts&h=eb1d216c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fbe7171f3ef4719a97722711f8a21846dba48ee","tid":27041,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"印尼係極少數有天災我會開心既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a950f9d46aea8336244e59bc63b5d61b06be861","tid":27041,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"又海嘯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168c8d1f1b0fbc1d02948f5f4abbe1e2299630f4","tid":27041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又海嘯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有都唔會幾高呢個強度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f679da06e00d5260d503a9c5bbc19f5169843280","tid":27041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"At least 92 people were killed and hundreds injured after an earthquake measuring 6.4 on the Richter scale hit Indonesia's Aceh province<br />\n<br />\n增至92人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1744217154f161ee178e660c600c87faa91d3c","tid":27041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a70bmpwx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa70bmpwx&h=57562113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8cp7h4of\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8cp7h4of&h=01a98117&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebfc46cb5e4f7fe1d38870ec7e20a4071bc86441","tid":27041,"uid":10139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印尼係極少數有天災我會開心既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9108806c174a2959b0cf8260ccddf08f4dbfa4d","tid":27041,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"印尼蘇門答臘北部亞齊特區發生的6級以上地震，增至97人死亡，2百多人受傷。有外電引述文件指，2百多座建築物嚴重受損或者倒塌，包括十多間清真寺，多條道路出現裂痕，有電線桿倒下。<br />\n<br />\n當局出動重型機械挖掘可能被埋在瓦礫的人，估計死傷人數會上升。<br />\n<br />\n地震在本港時間早上6時左右發生，震央距離亞齊特區首府班達亞齊約90公里，震源深度10公里，當局並無發出海嘯警告。<br />\n<br />\n印尼在2004年發生9級地震，引發南亞海嘯，造成23萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n97<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeee9490d6e1a57ade508441b7fb02c93c3ddd28","tid":27041,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"香港人偽善到仆街<br />\n日本地震就係咁捐錢"},{"pid":"52e94df17fac8015dbc7c8c8f7fbbb2bb3b3f107","tid":27041,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人偽善到仆街<br />\n日本地震就係咁捐錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔明點解東南亞d人種硬係睇落好似冇咁重要 所以激唔起我同理心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都想改變下心態 有冇心理醫生介紹下"}]}